{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/pullrequests/438/comments/66765658.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/sdformat/diff/osrf/sdformat:4661ad5586d3..1f9b76e5f6e6?path=cmake%2FDefaultCFlags.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat/pull-requests/438/_/diff#comment-66765658"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 438, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/pullrequests/438.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat/pull-requests/438"}}, "title": "removal of boost"}, "content": {"raw": "I don\u2019t know if it\u2019s necessary to use it, but CMake provides a variable for setting the C\\+\\+ Standard:\n\n[https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.1/variable/CMAKE\\_CXX\\_STANDARD.html](https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.1/variable/CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD.html)\n\nWhich ends up looking like:\n\n    set(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD 11) \n    set(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD_REQUIRED ON)\n\n\u200c", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I don\u2019t know if it\u2019s necessary to use it, but CMake provides a variable for setting the C++ Standard:</p>\n<p><a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.1/variable/CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.1/variable/CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD.html</a></p>\n<p>Which ends up looking like:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>set(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD 11) \nset(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD_REQUIRED ON)\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>\u200c</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-06-11T15:45:58.246311+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Carroll", "uuid": "{17dbbc15-cbc0-42f0-a985-cde9061c78a0}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B17dbbc15-cbc0-42f0-a985-cde9061c78a0%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B17dbbc15-cbc0-42f0-a985-cde9061c78a0%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:65740f22-cc56-4418-9608